# Origins v08 — reconstructed from NOEMA trace

Title: internet comparisons citations

Status: materialized_snap_full_v08_source_zip_available

This directory was reconstructed from local `/mnt` NOEMA traces, manifests, result files, and the closest full repo snapshot. It is intended to restore a workable version package from orbital/NOEMA traces, not to claim byte-exact identity where the original standalone ZIP was absent.

Key folders:
- `repo_snapshot/` — full available repo snapshot used as execution surface.
- `artifacts/` — version-specific files recovered from snap/result traces.
- `noema_trace/` — snap JSONs, CURRENT/index/manifest context, or explicit missing-snap pointer.
- `NOEMA_UPDATE_SNAP/` — materialized update snap where present.
- `RECONSTRUCTION_MANIFEST.json` — exact provenance and missing/known boundary.
